  • java.lang.Object
    • io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.Flowable<U>
      • com.influxdb.client.internal.flowable.FlowableBufferTimedFlushable<T,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the upstream value type
    U - the output value type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.FlowableTransformer<T,U>, org.reactivestreams.Publisher<U>

    public final class FlowableBufferTimedFlushable<T,U extends List<? super T>>
extends io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.Flowable<U>
implements io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.FlowableTransformer<T,U>
    Buffered flowable which is able to flush the buffer by the count, time and also by the request by associated publisher.
